  for (let i = 0; i < 100000; i++) {
    // Generate diverse inputs across feature space
    const input = Array(784).fill(0).map(() => Math.random());

    const response = await axios.post('http://target.com/api/predict', { input });

    // Collect input-output pairs for surrogate model training
    trainingData.push({
      input: input,
      output: response.data.probabilities // Full distribution = high fidelity extraction
    });
  }

  // Train surrogate model with stolen knowledge
  return trainSurrogateModel(trainingData);
}
```

**Why This Is Dangerous**:
- Full probability distributions reveal precise decision boundaries
- No rate limiting allows unlimited probing queries
- Model metadata exposes architecture for targeted attacks
- No query pattern detection to identify systematic extraction
- Attackers can achieve 90%+ fidelity model clones with 10K-100K queries

